strings.name: Les Femmes Leaders de ISM/Kolda
strings.description: YouthMappers chapter at Institut Supérieur de Management Kolda
strings.extendedDescription: Les Femmes Leaders de ISM/Kolda is an all-female mapping group in southern Senegal looking to put Kolda and surrounding villages on the map and better understand how to use OSM.
